      • combine

        public static ParameterSet combine(IParameterSet primary,
                                   IParameterSet... others)
        Combines parameter sets. The order of the sets is important: Parameters in sets more on the left take precedence over parameters sets to the right. That is, the most significant parameter set is the primary set.
        Parameters:
        primary - The primary set
        others - other parameter sets. Can be mixed with null values.
        Returns:
        A new, combined set.
